Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.70,0:00:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣 一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.95,0:00:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便去一趟防火水槽好麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.87,0:00:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那哪是女高中生該「順便」去的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.37,0:00:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了 麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.25,0:00:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的時候要不要順便去趟大工咖啡店？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.30,0:00:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點餐系統什麼的有些變化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.01,0:00:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對麻衣來說可能有些難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.76,0:00:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.64,0:00:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以教你各種各樣的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.03,0:00:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻… 麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.95,0:00:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.37,0:00:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Asymmetry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.37,0:00:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}註：非對稱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.29,0:00:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 雖說是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.62,0:00:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是唯心式非對稱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:00:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越了時髦的經典了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛我是在裝傻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.13,0:01:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投球太過全力了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.27,0:01:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都是贏家啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天在…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.65,0:01:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣的一方吶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.56,0:03:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的飯菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔥好像便宜一些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要用蔥做點菜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是博士她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜歡吃蔥啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.65,0:03:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃～ 名乃～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.45,0:03:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我抓到一隻烏鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危險啊 手會被啄到的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不在這裡麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道什麼時候圍巾沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是烏鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.43,0:04:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後 請您記住我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸虧是一隻懂禮貌的烏鴉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是烏鴉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙您誇獎 是我的光榮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝草莓牛奶麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝的話很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚊子？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我們殺蟲什麼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:04:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:04:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不過是在做該做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:04:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是烏鴉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生 圍巾哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有圍巾的話就不知道你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來聽聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.22,0:05:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是想要我的圍巾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 難道你把阪本先生的圍巾給烏鴉帶上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 真不光彩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那樣的話阪本先生就很可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我去做去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是Biscuit 1號
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟圍巾沒關！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:05:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說博士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Biscuit 1號 有什麼機能呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏鴉 問得好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.65,0:06:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有Rocket Punch機能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那來了哦——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射 光當！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博 博士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該給阪本先生做 做圍巾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為還有左手的啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射 光當！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這些傢伙殺死！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真的是非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有點過於淘氣了吶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.15,0:06:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個圍巾就請還給阪本先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只有很短的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:06:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但能說人類的話我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.62,0:06:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏鴉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.66,0:07:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走 烏鴉！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有機會的話再見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.63,0:07:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 大家保重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you again！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏鴉！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.64,0:07:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我拿走啦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\c&HD6A6FE&\pos(622,498)}與愛有關的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦… 課長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不信任我麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全面信任課長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 那就助我一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:07:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.48,0:12:19.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\pos(800,360)\shad3\4c&HE2DEE5&}體\N育\N館\N後\N1
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天在體育館後面挖了一個陷阱還放進去了黏合劑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這封信把她叫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.15,0:12:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她掉到陷阱裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs36\shad0\bord0\c&H2E2E2E&\pos(442,389)\frz13.348}Dear\N\h\h東雲 名乃 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天把你捕獲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東雲名乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.82,0:12:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.37,0:13:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到 櫻井誠竟是櫻井老師的弟弟啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做點什麼 問出來點櫻井老師的訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.72,0:13:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能玩圍棋足球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦誒 櫻井
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有現在 在交往的男朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No Future!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這個男人 我這個男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是沒有… 倒是沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:13:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦——！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好勒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好勒～～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個——…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才就當我沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在玩圍棋足球嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我倒是在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡我家的老姐麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說… 說什麼蠢話哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是身為圍棋足球部的前輩才問一下的啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 你也有玩過圍棋足球嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那必須的喲！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我高中可是MVP來的哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我們圍棋足球部現在沒有顧問
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果來做我們的顧問的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於我家老姐的事我可以全面協助哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.96,0:14:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢…不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了並不是… 喜歡嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不來做顧問的話 我就將老師喜歡姐姐的事情傳出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:14:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要來做顧問嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不來做嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.19,0:15:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.19,0:15:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顧問好麻煩…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦誒 大家聽我說啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}這就行動了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要… 要去追咯！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在體育館後面 中之條君被埋起來了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒——！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你馬上來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦誒 高崎先生他啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著啊… 聽好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中之條啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒被埋著！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒——！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啦！！說不定是一桿進洞！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒——！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是頭髮被剃光了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒——！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫上去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.02,0:15:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒——！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試試
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.48,0:15:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒——！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒——！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 怎麼回事啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦誒 喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起被埋起來 管理暴露他人隱私的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更應該是身為教育者的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼吶！！ 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教育者啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高崎老師！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有說哦——
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顧問 等著你來當！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這傢伙～～！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安中！！走吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是 教師吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是順勢而為
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.27,0:16:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過把頭髮剃下來了真是抱歉吶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.89,0:16:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去幫幫他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.19,0:16:36.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\shad3\4c&HE2DEE5&\pos(1100,360)}體\N育\N館\N後\N2
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正他也不知道是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.28,0:16:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}啊咧？啊咧咧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.32,0:16:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.32,0:16:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪裡啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動不了啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.54,0:16:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎怎怎怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.92,0:16:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:16:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,swim swim
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鯊魚鯊魚啪嗒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鯊魚鯊魚啪嗒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.14,0:17:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話就是這樣噠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad5\4c&HBBC1BC&\c&H44A030&\fad(0,1000)}琪{\c&H12C6E7&}琪 {\c&H1900B9&}是{\c&H8476F6&}這{\c&H9E9250&}個{\c&H4C6356&}樣{\c&H8945C9&}子{\c&HB2AD76&}的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吐槽你的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.81,0:18:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底 本來就是麻衣不好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機械似的不停的裝傻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直一直 都是我在吐槽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話就會陷入裝傻與吐槽的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無限循環？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是少女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 本該是閉月羞花的少女哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連像普通女高中生該有的對話都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天開始 一定不會吐槽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意志比鑽石都堅硬啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祐 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣 早上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W眼鏡！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs33\pos(545,655)}雙重
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強烈！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.77,0:18:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好強烈！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.98,0:18:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有今天格外強烈！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不能輸！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們之間要有所改變！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣 selamat pagi
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}註：印尼語早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 現在就是讓我們的女生對話之花綻放的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶 麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的「筋肉輓歌」看了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.67,0:19:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪哪哪 哪邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡 眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼高頻的裝傻是怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直像是在等著我的吐槽…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能吐槽哦 小祐！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是陷阱！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊水上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶了兩副眼鏡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中這混蛋——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我的吐槽…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.66,0:19:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我被允許吐的… 最高級槽給！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 不對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那並不是我的吐槽啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:19:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天第一堂課是國語來的麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來理科的中村好像倒了哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 沒關係吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了 今天第一堂課是國語來的麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對！ 剛才不是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危險——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這姑娘為什麼同樣的台詞說了兩次？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超可怕啊 這姑娘！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值日生 喊號
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.15,0:20:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起立
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請左
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 開始上課了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}開啟第82頁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請左什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請左什麼的算什麼啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且全員完全無視啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那… 有人想讀一下麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.38,0:20:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻… 麻衣！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 水上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.26,0:20:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}山在陰影中很是寂靜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.81,0:21:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而… 而且
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}村中燈火點點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在讀就說明——
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}初次來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在讀就說明…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說明…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說明…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,2000)}全背下來了啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.19,0:21:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吐槽什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.15,0:21:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.78,0:21:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服 啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.59,0:22:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話這麼大聲 對不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.35,0:22:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去走廊站著！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.39,0:22:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 這樣就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.19,0:22:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 這是我的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.19,0:22:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.99,0:22:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也因為這是麻衣的道路——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.53,0:22:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.83,0:22:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實從今天早晨開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就帶了隱形眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.17,0:22:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡 不是沒意義嘛！！
